.TH "tomoyo_get_absolute_path" 9 "tomoyo_get_absolute_path" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
tomoyo_get_absolute_path \- Get the path of a dentry but ignores chroot'ed root.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "char *" tomoyo_get_absolute_path
.BI "(const struct path *path "  ","
.BI "char * const buffer "  ","
.BI "const int buflen "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "path" 12
Pointer to "struct path".
.IP "buffer" 12
Pointer to buffer to return value in.
.IP "buflen" 12
Sizeof \fIbuffer\fP.
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Returns the buffer on success, an error code otherwise.

If dentry is a directory, trailing '/' is appended.
